The gesture algorithms in
  RxBlazorV2.MudBlazor/wwwroot/SwipeoutSortable.js
are derived from Framework7's swipeout and sortable components:
  - Swipeout: elasticity model, velocity snap thresholds, overswipe detection,
    swipe-to-delete sweep, action-button reveal layout.
  - Sortable: midpoint-cross sibling shift algorithm, tap-hold activation timing,
    edge auto-scroll, dragged-item snap-back.

The original Framework7 implementation uses jQuery / dom7 and Touch Events.
The port here is a clean re-implementation in plain DOM with Pointer Events for
mouse/pen and Touch Events for finger input.

