The cross-list group API in MudSortableSwipeoutListRx (SortableGroup with
Name / Pull / Put rules, drag-out-to-remove, clone semantics) follows the
SortableJS group model, with the BlazorSortable wrapper as a reference for
Blazor JS-interop conventions. No code is copied verbatim.
